== Presentation ==
This is ''Gallery'', a template that create a false gallery on miraheze.
It uses a loop to add as much image as stated in '''Number of Images''' (by default, it is one).
For each image, the template will dynamically the 3 same settings followed by the number of the image: 
- '''Name''' is the name of the file.
- '''Legend''' is a bit of text that will be on the bottom right of the zoomed image.
- '''Size''' is the size of the image on the page (before zoomed).

The CSS used can be found under Gallery.

== Code ==
<pre>
{{Gallery
|Number of Images= <!--By default, 1-->
|-
|Name 1= 
|Legend 1=
|Size 1=
|+ <!--Add one more group of parameters for each image (don't forget the number-->
}}
</pre>
